Advertise your product or brand here
contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

15:05.387 --> 15:06.520
Hello, pretty bird.

15:09.591 --> 15:12.159
(screeching)

15:12.227 --> 15:13.594
(screams)

15:16.565 --> 15:19.433
Oh, stan, I hope
you don't get lost in there.

15:19.501 --> 15:21.002
What if you die? (gasps)

15:21.069 --> 15:23.571
I left my soda in the freezer.

15:24.773 --> 15:27.341
Francine! Let's do some shots!

15:27.409 --> 15:29.844
Klaus?!
What are you doing in here?

15:29.911 --> 15:31.612
Stan put me in here
two days ago.

15:31.680 --> 15:33.981
The only reason
I didn't freeze to death is

15:34.049 --> 15:36.684
I filled my bowl with
that bottle of vodka.

15:36.752 --> 15:38.452
Why'd he put you
in the freezer?

15:38.520 --> 15:40.721
Oh, I'll tell you why.
He... (vomits)

15:56.838 --> 15:58.272
Hey, chocodile,
watch where you're going.

15:59.508 --> 16:02.176
Oh, hell no. (roars)

16:03.312 --> 16:04.845
(grunting)

16:10.986 --> 16:12.186
(glass clanks)

16:17.159 --> 16:18.793
(air hisses)

16:19.394 --> 16:21.128
Buh-bye.

16:21.196 --> 16:22.930
(sighs)

16:22.998 --> 16:24.598
Francine:
You bastard!

16:24.666 --> 16:26.834
(gasps) francine?!

16:29.171 --> 16:31.639
Francine,
what are you...?

16:31.707 --> 16:33.207
Klaus told me you've
been poisoning roger

16:33.275 --> 16:35.643
Just because you don't want to
spend time alone with me!

16:35.711 --> 16:37.111
Um...

16:37.179 --> 16:39.947
Forget it, stan!
I'm gonna get roger out,

16:40.015 --> 16:41.682
And then when we get home,

16:41.750 --> 16:44.085
You can have
all the alone time you want

16:44.152 --> 16:46.220
Because I'm not gonna
be there!

16:46.288 --> 16:47.488
Francine, wait!

16:47.556 --> 16:49.757
It's dangerous in here.

16:52.427 --> 16:54.261
Francine!

16:57.499 --> 16:59.333
Francine!

17:07.876 --> 17:11.479
(anguished groaning)

17:11.546 --> 17:12.913
Who are you?

17:12.981 --> 17:15.549
(high-pitched, weak voice):
Roger's conscience.

17:15.617 --> 17:18.018
Oh, my god,
you're dying of neglect!

17:18.086 --> 17:22.021
Kill... Me!

17:22.089 --> 17:23.523
(groaning)

17:23.592 --> 17:24.592
Tom skerritt?!

17:24.659 --> 17:26.926
(weakly):
Get me work.

17:30.465 --> 17:34.034
Oh, my, is it time
to change already?

17:34.102 --> 17:38.205
Yep, time to peel outta
these old dungarees.

17:38.273 --> 17:39.306
Steve:
You boys ready

17:39.374 --> 17:41.675
For that swim test
today, or what?

17:46.948 --> 17:48.816
(boys yelling)

17:48.884 --> 17:51.852
Look at us, fellas!
The underwear works!

17:51.920 --> 17:53.154
Just like clyde
said it would!

17:53.221 --> 17:54.889
Put 'em in
the girls' cabin!

17:54.956 --> 17:56.257
They're so impressed,

17:56.324 --> 17:58.025
They're bringing us
straight to their women!

17:58.093 --> 17:59.059
(screams)

17:59.127 --> 18:00.261
(all scream)

18:00.328 --> 18:01.829
If only we
could thank

18:01.897 --> 18:04.565
That magical mystery
underwear salesman.

18:04.633 --> 18:07.268
Oh, I don't think we've seen
the last of him.

18:14.976 --> 18:16.043
(train whistle blows)

18:22.918 --> 18:24.718
(gasps) it's breathtaking.

18:28.156 --> 18:29.323
(birds chirping)

18:29.391 --> 18:31.292
The cherry blossoms,
the rolling hills,

18:31.359 --> 18:33.294
The three urkels grazing
in the meadow.

18:38.600 --> 18:41.035
(sign buzzing)

18:41.102 --> 18:42.303
Francine!

18:44.706 --> 18:46.674
No, no, I'll
never tell anyone.

18:46.741 --> 18:49.543
Your reputation is
safe with me.

18:51.079 --> 18:52.680
Hey, fellas, I nailed her!

18:52.747 --> 18:54.148
It was so easy!

18:54.216 --> 18:56.150
(creature bellows, sobs)

19:02.224 --> 19:05.759
I am vicki: Voice
input child identicant.

19:05.827 --> 19:06.861
What are tears?

19:06.928 --> 19:08.028
Next!

19:11.867 --> 19:13.367
(horn blares)

19:13.435 --> 19:15.069
Learn how to drive,
you bitch!

19:15.136 --> 19:18.205
Relax, mc raw g.
Let it go.

19:18.273 --> 19:21.075
Are you kidding?
Nobody cuts off
biggie smalls!

19:21.142 --> 19:22.309
(tires screeching)

19:22.377 --> 19:24.245
Hey, jackass, you want
some of this?!

19:24.312 --> 19:25.246
(gun hammer cocks)

19:25.313 --> 19:27.581
(gunshots)

19:27.649 --> 19:29.383
(tires squeal away)

19:33.255 --> 19:35.856
He said he made this for me.

19:35.924 --> 19:37.358
Stan:
No, you don't get it.

19:37.425 --> 19:40.561
Francine and I haven't been
alone together in 18 years.

19:40.629 --> 19:42.730
What if she thinks I'm boring
and leaves me?

19:44.165 --> 19:45.499
Is that true?

19:45.567 --> 19:48.969
Is that why you were afraid
to be alone with me?

19:49.037 --> 19:51.305
Because you thought
I'd be bored with you?

19:51.373 --> 19:53.307
(sheepishly):
Well, yeah.

19:53.375 --> 19:55.576
Stan, you might
not be interesting,

19:55.644 --> 19:57.711
But you're definitely
not boring.

19:57.779 --> 20:00.514
I mean, the kids
have only been gone
for two days,

20:00.582 --> 20:03.551
And look at us, we're inside
an alien's brain.

20:03.618 --> 20:05.986
So, you're not gonna
sit down to dinner

20:06.054 --> 20:08.455
And realize
you don't wanna be
with me anymore?

20:08.523 --> 20:10.691
No, honey.
I know who you are.

20:10.759 --> 20:12.426
And I love you.

20:12.494 --> 20:13.427
Both:
Mm...

20:13.495 --> 20:16.030
Come on.
Let's go get roger.

20:23.572 --> 20:26.407
No, francine.
He needs a prince.

20:30.178 --> 20:32.646
(frantic moaning)

20:32.714 --> 20:34.415
(spits)
what the hell are you doing?!

20:34.482 --> 20:36.684
Me? You're the one
making a move.

20:36.751 --> 20:38.519
I was just napping
on this pedestal

20:38.587 --> 20:40.888
In the perfect light in
my most prettiest dress.

20:40.956 --> 20:42.923
Roger, you're in a coma.

20:42.991 --> 20:45.926
We're in your brain
to help you wake up
and bring you home.

20:45.994 --> 20:47.194
Home?

20:47.262 --> 20:48.829
You mean... Your home?

20:48.897 --> 20:49.964
That's right.

20:50.031 --> 20:51.465
Oh, thank god!
I hated my apartment.

20:51.533 --> 20:54.301
I don't know if you noticed,
but it didn't have a bathroom.

20:54.369 --> 20:55.903
I won't be getting that security
deposit back.

20:58.139 --> 21:00.007
Hey, guess who I had
lunch with today.

21:00.075 --> 21:01.208
Tom skerritt.

21:01.276 --> 21:02.943
Oh, that's interesting.

21:03.011 --> 21:06.447
Oh, yeah.
I guess it is.

21:06.514 --> 21:08.549
Buh-bye!

